        public void makeAction​(int[] movesOnEnergy)
        Makes Animal to take some action If Animal energyLevel equals 0 Animal dies If Animal is sleeping and energyLevel still is less then 4 sleep longer If Animal is sleeping ane energyLevel is now more then 4 wake up the Animal If Animal is not sleeping but energyLevel is less then 4 Animal fall asleep with 70% probability If Animal despire to low energyLevel did't fall asleep make one move If Animal has higher energyLevel make all moves allowed in this energyLevel
        Specified by:

        Parameters:
